DTSTART:20260429T203000Z
DTEND:20260429T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 11 - Assassinate the Führer DLC
DESCRIPTION:A high-stakes mission awaits. Precision, patience, and timing
 will be everything - and yes, the pressure is on. In the dark days of the
 end of World War 2 amidst the ruins of Berlin, one bullet can change
 history... Elite sniper Karl Fairburne returns to the front line in the
 remaster of this award-winning stealth-action experience. Packed with new
 features, contemporary visuals and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rkLLwGIpuw
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23152211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260409T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260506T112100Z
DTSTART:20260430T203000Z
DTEND:20260430T223000Z
SUMMARY:Crime Scene Cleaner | Ep. 12 - Act 2 Begins... The Bucket Is Ready
DESCRIPTION:We're back on cleanup duty! New scenes, new messes, and a
 bucket that's about to see things it can never unsee. Once you get tangled
 with the mob, you will forever be a part of the mob. At least they pay a
 decent salary and all you have to do is clean up after their dirty work,
 but you know what you're doing. So clean crime scenes, earn as much money
 as you can, and get ready for the next mission.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GHYyi9zluRk
CATEGORIES:Crime Scene Cleaner
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23162211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260410T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260506T112100Z
DTSTART:20260501T203000Z
DTEND:20260501T223000Z
SUMMARY:Red Dead Redemption II | Ep. 12 - You Either Ride On or Get Left
 Behind
DESCRIPTION:The frontier pushes forward. Tough choices, shifting
 loyalties, and a world that doesn't wait for anyone. Arthur Morgan and the
 Van der Linde Gang are outlaws on the run. With federal agents and bounty
 hunters massing on their heels, the gang must rob, steal, and fight their
 way across the rugged heartland in order to survive.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A9R4GvjD-SE
CATEGORIES:Red Dead Redemption II
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23172211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260411T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260506T112100Z
DTSTART:20260502T203000Z
DTEND:20260502T223000Z
SUMMARY:Fallout 4 | Ep. 46 - Nuka-World: Still Not the Vacation I Was
 Promised
DESCRIPTION:Back to Nuka-World... again. It's still dangerous, still
 chaotic, and still somehow drawing us back in. As the sole survivor of
 Vault 111, you enter a world destroyed by nuclear war. Every second is a
 fight for survival, and every choice is yours. Only you can rebuild and
 determine the fate of the Wasteland. Welcome home.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DU6WGoawsyo
CATEGORIES:Fallout 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
