SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 30 - Concrete Pump vs Me, Round 12
DESCRIPTION:Back on site! Time to fix, rebuild, and figure out what
 exactly went wrong. Expect machinery, progress, and at least one \"that
 wasn't supposed to happen\" moment. Construction Simulator is back -
 bigger and better than ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of
 them brand new to the franchise, and build to your heart's content on two
 huge maps - on your own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fVcRUlWm-eo
CATEGORIES:Construction Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
